Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:22.46,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沉睡的蓝色水之星 轻轻地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:31.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吻那点燃生命之火的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:36.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称为时间的金色波纹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:44.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在宇宙之唇中诞生的叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:52.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋在心中的温柔星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:56.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相唤起火焰……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:01:02.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同流离在波涛中的遇难船一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:07.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:16.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 现在有人正在寻找你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想与你相见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:48.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Oh 我禁不住相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.35,0:22:54.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}一定会和你再见面 从那天起就一直坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.94,0:23:00.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}一定能呼唤到你 如果你还有心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:10.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}无限的力量 将你唤醒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:16.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}啊 在你受到伤害前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:22.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}尽量 找寻 请
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:27.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}不要丢弃 正是因为在这痛苦的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:30.91,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}总有一天会看见蔚蓝的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.91,0:23:37.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}一定的 直到和你一起看的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜入朱庇特利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说敌舰在Side 2附近集结
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:01:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯瓦特罗大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:02:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于只有大尉一个人从地球回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在有各种各样的传言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来打算过几天再告诉你们两位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.74,0:02:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传言是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱克斯准将已经去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们没有时间悲伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在迂回至Side 2之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.05,0:02:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个作战方案必须要执行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的战场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膝盖的装甲也要赶紧拆除
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在敌舰旁边捡到的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说要使它能动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是强人所难
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 格雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.82,0:02:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作慢一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种旧式的能动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求看起来像勇士就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:51.67,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}勇士（Gelgoog）：一年战争时期吉翁军最后的量产型MS，编号MS-14A。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面基本上是解体之后维护用的雷姆零件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:02:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然怎么可能动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:02:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 它只能用来当监视哨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能进行战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你没听说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚少尉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚少尉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚少尉要驾驶勇士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜入朱庇特利斯号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱庇特利斯 是那个在木星的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我不是说过不需要步枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚小姐 和加布罗那次一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪 你好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花 看见蕾柯亚少尉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉她正领着柯瓦特罗大尉带来的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在参观战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚小姐要潜入敌军战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜入是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要做的事情不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚小姐一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:03:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 你们喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要潜入朱庇特利斯是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪 这是任务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加布罗那次 你差一点就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个任务很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那个时候幸亏得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是您志愿要去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您更加珍惜自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你已经长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思 蕾柯亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要总是把我当成孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是突然跟人顶撞 所以才把你当孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚小姐有她自己的决心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想有活跃的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪你也没有时间担心别人的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您上次去了加布罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次要去朱庇特利斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次最终是白去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您被认出是奥古的人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手很专业的 不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好在平安归来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 当时加布罗正在搬迁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间理会一个间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对卡缪说得太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪很迟钝的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然勾起少尉在加布罗的屈辱回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不要这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅塔斯就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我适合担当这种任务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才选了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚少尉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好不要多想哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然她还不是一个成熟的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 卡缪你还是跟那个人般配
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胡说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没到逞那份强的年纪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这地方瞎晃悠什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里都可以说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉为了逃避痛苦 才会参加这次作战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才会担心她胡来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么认真会给她添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 如果你现在想帮助蕾柯亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会往她的伤口上撒盐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花 蕾柯亚小姐毕竟是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不可能有少女一般的感伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白这次作战的意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想占领Side 2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:08:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且夺取能和莎拉一起在地球圈漫步的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布提马斯大人想得到大地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论我多么适应木星的环境
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我毕竟是从女性体内诞生的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您希望改造地球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我想得到那个栖身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是殖民卫星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你帮助我 莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回朱庇特利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉在多戈斯·基亚待命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会用Z高达作为蕾柯亚小姐的后方支援
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:08:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 潜入由我一个人去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉 你离开朱庇特利斯之后前往Side 2的空域
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再差的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也应该能和奥古的舰队碰头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你成功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没潜入就说逃脱的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪机 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱德舰长 为什么让卡缪出击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是蕾柯亚少尉一个人去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从作战的角度来说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Z的后方支援可能是浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是考虑到蕾柯亚少尉的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱德舰长的举措是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要从男性的角度考虑问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是军队 不分男女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是作为一个军人之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚少尉首先是一个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等和平之后你再这么想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汉肯舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回拉迪什吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子就是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.59,0:10:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也去负责蕾柯亚少尉的后方支援吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了使你提起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真蛮横啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下达命令的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花园丽军曹 驾驶梅塔斯出击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是MS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正向朱庇特利斯的方位进发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然无视我舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 需要我出击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不知道是敌是友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是追击巴布提马斯大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一有什么事的话 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:11:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你出击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据情报 那是一艘单独行动的飞船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然驾驶这种旧式旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算卖多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像是复制品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种机体在爱好者中很有人气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你估计要花多少钱才能使它恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试运行虽然没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你得加满燃料才能飞行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我计算过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃料消耗比想象中的严重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检查完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台MS不过是个普通玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便进行身体检查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想和滥用职权的男人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经由女兵检查过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪个卫星的移民啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人就是巴布提马斯·西洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经过了30分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 蕾柯亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是Z高达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那台MA应该是那个男的驾驶的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你想伤害巴布提马斯大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种功率的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布提马斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个声音…莎拉·扎比亚罗夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在开发新型MS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 从小行星带去往地球圈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是那个阿克西斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算和提坦斯接触吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之一句话 吉翁和提坦斯是一路的 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个穿标准服的 你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…我…迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你属于那个部分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.11,0:15:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人是刚才所报告的漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为扶手出了故障
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是我拿错扶手了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我你的名字 以及所属
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫蕾柯亚·朗特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在Side 2的85号卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 左舷15度方向发现炮火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敌袭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是MS之间的交战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚·朗特 祝你旅途愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 前提是你能回得去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人 知道我的真实身份吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你没有武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有步枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打倒你 为了那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花 你怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用榴弹发射器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花 不要勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是梅萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手机不明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Z高达
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感受到了那种压迫感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以莎拉的实力 二对一的负担太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫帕拉斯·雅典娜出击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:53.75,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉斯·雅典娜（Pallas Athene）：西洛克在木星制造的第2台MS，是一台重视攻击\N力的重型MS，其名称来源于古希腊神话中从主神宙斯（朱庇特）脑中全副武装诞生\N而出的女战神帕拉斯·雅典娜，编号PMX-001。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 你说要独自应战到底吗 莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱庇特利斯保持第一级战斗状态待命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉 你这家伙真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 听说现在能看见MS战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶奇怪的MS来的是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看见光了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱庇特利斯里面没有你这么漂亮的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的哦 不是奉承你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我不是个好女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 3号甲板的闸门打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有发出出击命令啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制员 怎么回事 控制员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蕾柯亚·朗特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个丫头想回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警卫在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只苍蝇不会有什么作为的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像喜欢上了那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西洛克的飞船…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被避开了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我被扰乱了 得冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台MA是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚少尉 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花 你怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功率正在下降
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真胡来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:19:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机抓得很准
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个不能留下活路的敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有一半的喷嘴被击毁了 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡缪 花 要离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟上来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅塔斯由我带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚小姐 请您先走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花 幸亏你来了 帮了大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到Z上来 戒备后方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经尽力了 但那台MS…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感受到一种和巴布提马斯大人不同的强大意念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.86,0:21:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经很努力了 干得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布提马斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去休息吧 莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还需要你为下次行动效劳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.96,0:21:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚少尉的观察力真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时拼命逃出来 所以不大清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请借我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记…记不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾柯亚少尉 你去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.33,0:22:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.14,0:22:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这毕竟是个陌生的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.78,0:22:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有把巴布提马斯·西洛克的事汇报给布莱德
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.30,0:22:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的蕾柯亚还不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事在蕾柯亚的心中留下了一个结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.66,0:23:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚历山大号对Side 2的卫星展开毒气攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.45,0:23:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星中的数百万生命面临危机
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.83,0:23:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱玛向着毒气罐挺进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.12,0:24:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其背后是大人们黑暗的瓜葛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.29,0:24:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士Zeta高达
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.53,0:24:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Side 2的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.73,0:24:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看见了时代之泪
